config.Fishing Difficulty.name: 钓鱼难度
config.Fishing Difficulty.description: 选择一个钓鱼小游戏的难度. Easy 简单模式: 难度降低 5% 至 100%. 轻松周末:周末当天的钓鱼难度降低 10% 到 30% . Hard 困难模式: 难度增加 5% 至 100%. NIGHTMARE 噩梦难度: 给想挑战高难度钓鱼的人! 关于动态天气设置, 请查看动态天气选项名字的提示条.
config.section.Fishing Minigame.name: 钓鱼游戏
config.= Dynamic Weather Info =.name: = 动态天气 =
config.= Dynamic Weather Info =.descript: 如果你在钓鱼难度中选择了动态天气, 钓鱼的难度将跟随天气变化. easy选项: 风季增加15%, 下雨降低10%,下雪降低15%,暴风雨降低20%.Easier选项将在此基础上在降低10%, Easiest选项降低20%.
config.= Dynamic Weather Info =.values.=: = 鼠标放到选项上有额外信息. =
config.All Times Of Day.name: 任意时间捕捉
config.All Times Of Day.description: 任意时间段都可以捕捉所有的鱼.
config.All Types Of Weather.name: 任意天气捕捉
config.All Types Of Weather.description: 除了传说鱼类，任意天气都可以捕捉所有的鱼.
config.All Seasons.name: 任意季节

config.Clean Waters/No Trash.name: 垃圾设置
config.Clean Waters/No Trash.description: 在钓鱼时删除或替换所有垃圾项目。无垃圾:钓鱼时完全禁用垃圾. 蟹笼替换: 用蟹笼产物替换垃圾 请注意，如果没有鱼产卵，偶尔的垃圾物品仍可能被打捞起来。该设置大大减少了垃圾的机会
config.Clean Waters/No Weeds.name: 藻类设置
config.Clean Waters/No Weeds.description: 在钓鱼时删除或替换海藻，绿藻和白藻, 没有藻类:在钓鱼时完全禁用藻类. 蟹笼替换: 用蟹笼产物替换藻类.
config.Crab Pots No Trash.name: 垃圾设置

config.Fishable Prismatic Shards (REQ).d: 五彩碎片鱼可以在大多数地方通过钓鱼获得。以下的配置需要勾选这项!
config.Prismatic Shard Sell Value.name: 售卖价格
config.Prismatic Shard Sell Value.descri: 五彩碎片鱼价格售价，该选项不要求勾选其他的五彩碎片选择.
config.Prismatic Shards Fish Tanks.name: 鱼缸功能
config.Prismatic Shards Fish Tanks.descr: 五彩碎片鱼能够被放入鱼缸中，该选项不要求勾选其他的五彩碎片选择!
config.Prismatic Shard Spawn Rate.name: 鱼上钩率
config.Prismatic Shard Spawn Rate.descri: 五彩碎片鱼的上钩率。需要勾选‘钓鱼捕获’.
config.Prismatic Shards On Farm.name: 农场钓鱼捕获
config.Prismatic Shards On Farm.descript: 能够在农场钓到五彩碎片鱼。需要勾选‘钓鱼捕获’!
config.Lucky Prismatic Shards.name: 根据幸运刷新
config.Lucky Prismatic Shards.descriptio: 五彩碎片鱼的上钩率根据电视报道的每日运气而变化，需要勾选‘钓鱼捕获’!
config.Prismatic Shards Weather.name: 天气刷新
config.Prismatic Shards Weather.descript: 五彩碎片鱼的只在雨天或者下雪天能够钓到，需要勾选‘钓鱼捕获’!
config.Prismatic Shards 7am To 9am.name: 五彩碎片鱼 上午7到9点 出现
config.Prismatic Shards 7am To 9am.descr: Prismatic Shards are now exclusive to the hours between 7AM and 9AM for catching, and this time frame can be combined with the other time settings. Please note that the Fishable Prismatic Shards (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect!
config.Prismatic Shards 12pm To 2pm.name: 五彩碎片鱼 中午12到2点 出现
config.Prismatic Shards 12pm To 2pm.desc: Prismatic Shards are now exclusive to the hours between 12PM and 2PM for catching, and this time frame can be combined with the other time settings. Please note that the Fishable Prismatic Shards (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect!
config.Prismatic Shards 11pm To 1am.name: 五彩碎片鱼 晚上11到1点 出现
config.Prismatic Shards 11pm To 1am.desc: Prismatic Shards are now exclusive to the hours between 11PM and 1AM for catching, and this time frame can be combined with the other time settings. Please note that the Fishable Prismatic Shards (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect!
